Package com.deezer.sdk.model Description

This package contains Java classes mapping objects returned by Deezer API.

When executing a DeezerRequest with a JsonRequestListener, the response is automatically parsed in one of the objects in this package, making it easier to use in an Android application.

When querying a list of objects (for instance, the tracks list of a playlist), the Deezer API might return only a limited number of items. Then the result is a PaginatedList, which contains the request url to fetch the next page of results.

To know more about these objects, check the Deezer API documentation
